app_description: Translate everywhere. Travel to any country and communicate with everyone around you. Voice translation is real time and easy. Translator Translate Voice will instantly translate and pronounce phrases from people you communicate with. Read and translate menus and signs with instant camera and photo translation. Get Translator Translate Voice now and stop spending time looking for phrases in the dictionary! Say any phrase and your digital voice translator will translate and speak translation back to you! Translator Translator Voice key features: Real time speech recognition and translation Voice recognition with end of speech detection Translation keyboard extension for messengers and other apps Translation with share extension Male and female realistic voice generation Photo translation Variable voice speed of generated speech Translation in 114 languages Translate photo from your library Real time voice translator Translator Translator Voice Pro features: Unlimited voice translation Instant camera and photo translation 100 Ads free Premium access: With upgrade to Translator Translator Voice Premium you will get unlimited full access to all features.
